      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Cycle threshold (Ct) in SARS-CoV-2 RT-PCR
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A guide for health protection teams about interpreting Ct in real-time, reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) assays performed for Sars-CoV-2.</p>

  </div>
</div>

